I've only called him, "Hama-chan."

88
00:05:34,100 --> 00:05:37,270
{\an8}I've never used polite language
since we've debuted.

89
00:05:37,337 --> 00:05:39,505
{\an8}We always used "kun"
with Akito and Junta.

90
