That's what makes him amazing.

92
00:05:45,011 --> 00:05:46,045
He's got talent.

93
00:05:46,112 --> 00:05:50,450
If I needed to talk to someone,
it would probably be Hama-chan.

94
00:05:50,516 --> 00:05:54,087
He's easy to talk to
and easy to get advice from.

95
00:05:54,153 --> 00:05:55,455
He's a great listener.

96
00:05:57,457 --> 00:06:00,827
<i>An adorable character
and the life of the party.</i>

97
