-I didn't know that.
-Yep.

144
00:09:27,500 --> 00:09:29,869
Okay, everyone,
please stop what you're doing.

145
00:09:29,936 --> 00:09:32,672
Staff members, please come here.

146
00:09:34,941 --> 00:09:37,810
I strained my back,

147
