is pretty rare to see.

227
00:14:45,217 --> 00:14:46,652
And he continues to grow.

228
00:14:46,719 --> 00:14:48,754
Kotaki absorbs everything.

229
00:14:49,855 --> 00:14:54,860
{\an8}<i>This power to absorb everything
has made him very successful as an actor.</i>

230
